properties.html:
Knights of Columbus

South County Council

It's a book that had a huge impact on me. I loved that as a shape for a novel: put a bunch of people in a beautiful place, give them all tuberculosis, make them all stay in a fur sleeping. 

We are Knights

serving Christ by serving other 

The South County Council membership consists mostly of parishioners from Our Lady of Sorrows Catholic Church (www.olos.us) in West River MD and Holy Family Catholic Church (www.holyfamilychurch.com) in Davidsonville MD.

The council donates funds to various charitable projects and members are active participants in their parishes and communities.

read more

Become a Knight

How to Join our Council

Ready to become a Knight? We're ready for you to join! 
Our focus is serving Christ by serving others, giving back to our community and fellowship with out brother Knights. We provide service to both Our Lady of Sorrows and Holy Family Catholic Churches in South Anne Arundel County by holding fund raisers for charities, set up for events and whatever Father asks. There are 3 degrees of Knight hood and all have thier own ceremony. Click below to read more about becoming a Knight of Columbus and our South County Council.

read more

Our events

We have multiple events, both service and social that all of our members can take part in. We hold an annual tootsie roll drive to benefit the Special School of South Counth, man the beer counter at the Ren Fest and have a great Christmas party/cookie exchange at the end of the year. Click the link below to view our events and add them to your calendar.
